============================================================
CONFIG REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Update root `.env.example`:

OPS_ENABLED=true
OPS_AUTOPILOT_ENABLED=true
OPS_AUTOPILOT_MODE=advisory
OPS_AUTOPILOT_DRY_RUN=true
OPS_AUTOPILOT_REQUIRE_APPROVAL=true
OPS_HEALTH_ANALYZER_ENABLED=true

INCIDENTS_ENABLED=true
INCIDENT_AUTO_CREATE=true
INCIDENT_AUTO_REMEDIATE=false
INCIDENT_REQUIRE_APPROVAL_FOR_REMEDIATION=true
INCIDENT_DEFAULT_SEVERITY=warning

SLA_ENABLED=true
SLA_DEFAULT_UPTIME_TARGET_PERCENT=99.5
SLA_DEFAULT_RESPONSE_TARGET_MINUTES=60
SLA_DEFAULT_RESOLUTION_TARGET_HOURS=24

MAINTENANCE_WINDOWS_ENABLED=true
CHANGE_MANAGEMENT_ENABLED=true
CHANGE_APPROVAL_REQUIRED=true

DISASTER_RECOVERY_ENABLED=true
DR_DRILL_DRY_RUN=true
DR_BACKUP_VALIDATION_ENABLED=true

FLEET_MANAGEMENT_ENABLED=true
FLEET_DEFAULT_ENVIRONMENT=local

INTEGRATIONS_ENABLED=true
INTEGRATIONS_DRY_RUN=true

WEBHOOKS_ENABLED=true
WEBHOOKS_DRY_RUN=true
WEBHOOK_SIGNING_SECRET=
WEBHOOK_DELIVERY_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=10
WEBHOOK_MAX_RETRIES=3

SIEM_EXPORT_ENABLED=true
SIEM_PROVIDER=mock
SIEM_DRY_RUN=true
SIEM_ENDPOINT=
SIEM_TOKEN=

TICKETING_ENABLED=true
TICKETING_PROVIDER=mock
TICKETING_DRY_RUN=true
TICKETING_ENDPOINT=
TICKETING_TOKEN=

SSO_ENABLED=false
SSO_PROVIDER=mock
SSO_DRY_RUN=true
OIDC_ISSUER_URL=
OIDC_CLIENT_ID=
OIDC_CLIENT_SECRET=
SAML_METADATA_URL=
SAML_ENTITY_ID=

SCIM_ENABLED=false
SCIM_DRY_RUN=true
SCIM_BEARER_TOKEN=

MANAGED_SERVICE_ENABLED=true
MSP_MODE=false
SUPPORT_CASES_ENABLED=true
CUSTOMER_HEALTH_ENABLED=true

RELEASE_CHANNELS_ENABLED=true
DEFAULT_RELEASE_CHANNEL=stable

Rules:
- Ops Autopilot must default to advisory and dry-run.
- Incident auto-remediation must be disabled by default.
- SSO/SCIM must be disabled by default.
- SIEM, webhook, and ticketing integrations must use mock/dry-run by default.
- Real integration mode requires explicit config and secrets.
- Missing integration config must fail safely.
- No token or secret may be logged or exposed in frontend.
- Any destructive remediation requires approval.

