Rules:
- Dry-run by default.
- Never restore over production database without explicit confirmation.
- Restore confirmation text:
  CONFIRM_RESTORE_DRILL
- No secrets in DR reports.
- DR drill results tenant-scoped where applicable.
- DR events must be audited.

