============================================================
API RESPONSE FORMAT
============================================================

All endpoints must use standard response shape:

Success:

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {},
  "error": null,
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Error:

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "message": "Human readable message"
  },
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Required error codes:

- OPS_DISABLED
- AUTOPILOT_BLOCKED
- INCIDENT_NOT_FOUND
- REMEDIATION_NOT_FOUND
- REMEDIATION_APPROVAL_REQUIRED
- REMEDIATION_BLOCKED
- SLA_DISABLED
- MAINTENANCE_WINDOW_NOT_FOUND
- CHANGE_NOT_FOUND
- CHANGE_APPROVAL_REQUIRED
- DRILL_CONFIRMATION_REQUIRED
- INTEGRATION_NOT_CONFIGURED
- INTEGRATION_DRY_RUN_ONLY
- WEBHOOK_NOT_FOUND
- WEBHOOK_SECRET_REQUIRED
- SIEM_NOT_CONFIGURED
- TICKETING_NOT_CONFIGURED
- SSO_NOT_CONFIGURED
- SCIM_DISABLED
- SUPPORT_CASE_NOT_FOUND
- MSP_PERMISSION_REQUIRED
- RELEASE_CHANNEL_NOT_FOUND
- TENANT_ACCESS_DENIED

