  -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"event_types": ["risk.halt.activated"], "dry_run": true}'

Run DR backup validation:

curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/ops/dr/backup-validation \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"dry_run": true}'

